Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.19,0:02:03.37,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}可曾记得？ 那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:13.32,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}涌上心头的 感动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:23.41,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}沐浴着湛蓝的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:27.77,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你迎风前行的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:34.45,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}让我陶醉时 目光相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:39.31,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我们齐声欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:46.58,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}就像那 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:53.36,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)\an3}无论何时 都想挥动双手的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:57.65,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}确实是 曾经
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:03.18,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}与你同在的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:07.53,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}永远如 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:17.32,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我们的前方 道路在延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:26.05,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}攀上 下一个陡坡后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:30.81,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)}我们再相见吧
